> Brennan.

And brown steering, brown turn signal/wiper switches, chrome bumpers, clock,
brown mats, red/brown seats with gold cloth inserts, two tone metallic paint.
They came as buses and Westies in 78 and 79.
Brad Clausen has 4 pics of the 78 Champagne Edition from the factory brochure
here:
http://webpages.charter.net/bclausen/78Bus/
Pic 2 shows the interior of the bus.
Pic 3 shows the brown plaid of the Westy, same plaid as 78/79 Dakota Beige
Westies.

